### If you want to recreate the GitHub repo

Use `wsm3d-full-backup.bundle` (173 MB at `C:\Users\koosh\_wsm3d_audit\wsm3d-full-backup.bundle`) to recreate `KooshaPari/WorldSphereMod`:

```bash
# On a fresh clone target:
git clone --bare https://github.com/yourname/WorldSphereMod.git wsm3d-restore
cd wsm3d-restore
git fetch C:/Users/koosh/_wsm3d_audit/wsm3d-full-backup.bundle 'refs/remotes/*:refs/remotes/*' '+refs/heads/*:refs/heads/*'
git push --all origin
git push --tags origin  # if any tags were in bundle
```

